    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230420/extras/8d5913ac22f37f3af8edf58352796d9e.poster.avif?t=1742984278\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230420/extras/8d5913ac22f37f3af8edf58352796d9e.webm?t=1742984278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230420/extras/8d5913ac22f37f3af8edf58352796d9e.mp4?t=1742984278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >&quot;The child has disappeared.&quot;</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, a mother who lost her child desperately follows the traces left behind. During her search, she hears a rumor about a malevolent spirit that preys only on children and resides in the ruins deep within the forest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clinging to the faintest hope, she tirelessly tracks down the place and finally arrives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just then, a familiar voice echoes from somewhere. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chasing the sound through the darkness, she soon finds herself trapped in an endless corridor with no way out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is only one way to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230420/extras/e3f9ddab69700a8d7376210dead1d7d1.poster.avif?t=1742984278\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230420/extras/e3f9ddab69700a8d7376210dead1d7d1.webm?t=1742984278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230420/extras/e3f9ddab69700a8d7376210dead1d7d1.mp4?t=1742984278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game rules</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Observe your surroundings carefully and explore thoroughly to uncover any anomalies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you find no clues, move on to the next stage. But if you notice something strange, head for the exit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They will try to deceive you by any means. Never let your guard down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Input</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movements : W, A, S, D</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Walk : Left Shift</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flashlight : F</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact : LMB</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uninteract : RMB</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rotation Reset : WMB</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
